-833f50c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C739 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1668%2C1108 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=2224%2C1478 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><img class=\"wp-image-559785 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--full no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2020/10/200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar-wings-833f50c.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C412\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Canyon CP0018 Aerocockpit wings diagram\" title=\"200907_Presskit_Aeroad_2021_EN_Handlebar wings\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> The wings of the CP0018 and CP0015 handlebars can be adjusted for fit or removed for travel.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Canyon</i></span></div>\n<p>Canyon founder Roman Arnold said: “Mathieu fortunately did not fall. We want to ensure with absolute certainty that no one comes to harm before we fully understand the root cause.”</p>\n<p>The company’s CEO, Armin Landgraf, added: “We are doing everything we can to equip affected Aeroad models as quickly as possible with a cockpit that meets both our and our customers’ demands for total quality and safety.”</p>","author":"George Scott","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"4694f5142ec66fe914833fa5084fab04805270c220640c021e63fc80a2a1981f","category":"Cycling"}